synthesis of decision rules.wdecision tables can be used as an effectivetool during an interview to record the logic of processes to be automated.  the result of such an interviewis not a structure of complete decision tables but rather sets of decision rules.  the purpose of thispaper is to provide a procedure for synthesizing the decision rules and thus provide an aid in developinga structure of complete decision tables.cacm july, cheng, c.rabin, j..kdecision rules, decision tables, logical tables,logical design, system design, specification language.c. .ca jb january ,   : pm